quran[431]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Mo laamu woni e juu…óe Mun On mawnii, ko Kanko woni hattan…óo kala huunde"
  67,2,"On tagir…óo maayde e nguurndam, fii ndaarndagol on ko hommbo e mo'on …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude golle. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, Haforoowo On"
  67,3,On tagu…óo kammuuli jee…ói…ói fawondir…ói. A yi'ataa …ďura-…ďurda e tagu Jom hinaraŇčke On. Yiltu ndaar…óe maa …óen (daaraa). Taw si a yi'ay ceekol
  67,4,"Refti ruttaa ndaar…óe …óen laa…ďi …ói…ói, gite maa …óen ruttoto e maa…óa hara ko …óe hoy…óe, ta∆īii…óe"
  67,5,"Gom…óii Men cu…óinirii kammu aduna ngun [koode] pitilli, Men wa…ói …óe fi…óir…óe seytanuuji, Men hebilani …ďe lette Hu…ď…ďunge negn"
  67,6,"Hino woodani …ďen yeddu…ďe Joomi mun, lette Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  67,7,"Si …ďe weddaama e nder magge, …ďe naniray nge haacaango, hara hinge fata"
  67,8,"Hinge e…ď…ďa fultagol, sabu tikkere nden. Tuma kala nde dental bugaa e magge, ayninaa…ďe nge …ďen lamndoo …ďe : \"E hara jertinoowo araano e mo'on"
  67,9,"∆Āe wi'a: \"Pellet ! Jertinoowo aruno e amen tigi, kono men fenni men wi'i: Allah jippinaali hay e huunde, on wonaali si wanaa e nder majjere mawnde"
  67,10,"∆Āe wi'ita : \"Si me…óen nanaynoo maa hara me…óen haqqilaynoo, men jeyetanooke e yim…ďe Hu…ď…ďunge ngen"
  67,11,∆Āe qirritii junuubi ma…ď…ďe …óin. Halakuyee woodanii jom en Hu…ď…ďaynge ngen
  67,12,"Pellet, huloo…ďe Joomi mun …ďen ka wirnii, hino woodani …ďen haforaneede e njo…ďdi mawndi"
  67,13,Suu…óee konngu…ói mon maa …ďanninon …óum. Kanko On ko O anndu…óo ko woni e nder …ďer…óe
  67,14,"E hara tagu…óo On anndaa? Ko Kanko le woni Newii…óo, Humpitii…óo On"
  67,15,"Ko Kanko wa…óani on leydi ndin eltaandi : haray yehee e seraaji mayri, √Īaamon e arsike Makko. Ko ka Makko woni ummital ngal"
  67,16,"E on hooli On won…óo ka kammu nde O munnataa e mo'on leydi ndin, Tawa yoo hindi dilla? @Corrected"
  67,17,Kaa on hooli On won…óo ka kammu nde O wurtataa e mon henndu bippooru? Aray nde anndon ko honno woni jertinaango Am ngon
  67,18,Sellii adinoo…ďe …ďen …óon …ďen fenniino. Taskii ko honno lette Am …óen wattinirnoo
  67,19,"E …ďee yi'aali colli …óin dow ma…ď…ďe, hi…ói fonta gabitannji …ói √Īobba? [Wonnde] jogitaaki …óin si wanaa Jom hinaraŇčke On. Pellet, ko O reenu…óo kala huunde"
  67,20,"E ko hommbo woni on konuujo mum wallata on hara wanaa Jom hinaraŇčke On? Tigi on, heefer…ďe …ďen wonaali si wanaa e nder hodo"
  67,21,"E ko hommbo woni arsikoowo on, si O jogitike arsike Makko on? Si ko woni, …ďe duumike e ∆īaggere e wo…ó…óitagol"
  67,22,Kere ko on yahoowo no hippi yeeso mun …ďuri feewude? Kaa ko on yahoowo no fotondiri e laawol focciingol
  67,23,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni ko fu…ó…ói on, O wa…óani on nan…óe e gii…óe e …ďer…óe\". Kono fan…óii ko yettoton [neema]"
  67,24,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni saakitu…óo on leydi, ko ka Makko kadi woni ko moo…ďitoyte…óon"
  67,25,"Hi…ďe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si tawii ko on goongu…ďe"
  67,26,"Maaku : \"Anndee anndugol [fii Darnagl] ko ka Allah woni. Min on ko Mi jertinoowo [tun] …ďanngina"
  67,27,"Nde …ďe yi'oyta (lette) …óen ka …ďadii, geece yeddu…ďe …ďen suni geece heefer…ďe, […ďe] wi'anee : \"Ko …óum …óoo woni ko …óa…ď…ďayno…óon"
  67,28,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si Allah ∆īettitii lam min e wonndii…ďe am maa O yurmaama men, ko hommbo da…óndata heefer…ďe …ďen lette muusu…óe"
  67,29,"Maaku : \"Ko Kanko Jom hinaraŇčke On. Men gom…óinii Mo, ko e Makko kadi men fawii. Aray nde anndon ko hommbo woni e majjere …ďanngunde"
  67,30,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si ndiyam mon …óam wattinii …ďee…ďu…óam, ko hommbo addanta on ndiyam ilay…óam"
  68,1,Nuun. Mi woondirii karambol e ko …ďe winndirta kon
  68,2,"Aan a wonaa, sabu neema Joomi maa on, haangaa…óo"
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodan-maa njo…ďdi ndi ta∆īondirtaa"
  68,4,"E ko pellet, hi…óa e jikku mawngu"
  68,5,"Aray nde tinaa, …ďe yi'a kam…ďe kadi"
  68,6,ko hommbo e mo'on woni haangaa…óo on
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa …ďuri anndude majju…óo on laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi …ďuri anndude feewu…ďe …ďen"
  68,8,Wata a tewto fennoo…ďe …ďen
  68,9,"Hi…ďe yi…ói si a newantono (…ďe), …ďe newano-(maa)"
  68,10,"Wata a tewto kadi kala …óuu…óu…óo woondugol, hoy…óo"
  68,11,"…óuu…óu…óo nyo*ugol, …óuu…óu…óo yaarugol baddi"
  68,12,"…óuu…óu…óo ha…óugol mo∆ī∆īere, jaggitoowo, bakkondin…óo"
  68,13,"yoora-…ďerndeejo e hoore …óum, he…ďiraa…óo nii"
  68,14,fii o wonii jom jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe
  68,15,"Si Aayeeje Amen …óen janngaama e [tawnde] makko, o wi'a: \"Ko tinndi adinoo…ďe"
  68,16,Aray nde Men maandina mo e hoore kinal
  68,17,"Men jarribor …ďe wano Men jarribornoo jey…ďe ngesa mba : fewndo …ďen woondunoo pellet, …ďe so√Īay mba subaka ko …ďe dawu…ďe"
  68,18,"…ďe ittintinaali [wiide] :\"Si Allah ja…ďii"
  68,19,Yiite immori ka Joomi maa ari huu…ďiti mba tawi hi…ďe …óaanii
  68,20,mba wa'iti wa jemma …ďaleejo
  68,21,∆Āe noddindiri bimmbi on
  68,22,"Kori dawee ka ngesa mon, si tawii ko on so√Īoo…ďe"
  68,23,∆Āe hucciti hi…ďe …ď…óuumbo
  68,24,"Wonnde \"Miskiino woo naatataa e mabba hannde"
  68,25,"∆Āe ndawidi e …óawugol [waasu…ďe …ďen] ko …ďe e…ď…ďu…ďe"
  68,26,"Nde …ďe yi'unoo mba, …ďe wi'i: \"Pellet, men majjii [laawol ngol]"
  68,27,wurin ko men …óawaa…ďe
  68,28,"∆Āur…óo …ďe mo∆ī∆īude on wi'i: \"Mi wi'anaano on : haanii ko subbunhino…óon"
  68,29,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Senaade woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari ko men too√Īu…ďe"
  68,30,"Wo…ó…ďe e ma…ď…ďe fewtiti …ďeya, hi…ďe felindira"
  68,31,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko men bewu…ďe"
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana men …ďuri mban …óon mo∆ī∆īude. Ko ka Joomi amen ko min reer…óube e [yaafeede]"
  68,33,"Ko non tigi woni lette …óen; ko lette laakara …óen non …ďuri manude, sinno hi…ďe anndunoo"
  68,34,"Pellet, hino woodani gom…óu…ďe …ďen ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, Aljannaaji neema"
  68,35,Kere Men wa…óay jebbilii…ďe …ďen wano bom…ďe …ďen
  68,36,"Ko he…ďi on, si …óon √Īaawira non"
  68,37,"Kaa hi…óon mari Deftere, nde janngoton e mun"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e mayre, ko ko su…ďoto…óon"
  68,39,"Kaa ko fodooje woodani on e Amen, hoolnii…óe haa √Ďalnde Darngal, wonnde pellet, hino woodani on ko √Īaawoton kon"
  68,40,Lamndii …ďe ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe fawtanii…ďe …óum
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidii…ďe woodani …ďe? Awa yo …ďe addu kafidii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, si tawii ko …ďe goongu…ďe"
  68,42,"√Ďalnde belenru √Īoroytee, …ďe noddee e sujjugol kono hara …ďe waawataa. @Corrected"
  68,43,"Hara gite ma…ď…ďe …óen no heli, koyeera no suddi …ďe. Ko tawde …ďe noddeteno e sujjugol fewndo ka …ďe waawunoo"
  68,44,Accidam e kala fennu…óo ndee yewtere; aray nde Men suynira …ďe nokku ka …ďe anndaa
  68,45,"Mi…óo nennan …ďe. Pellet non, pewje Am …óen ko tii…óu…óe"
  68,46,"Kaa a lamndi …ďe njo…ďdi, hara ko yo…ďugol ndi teddani …ďe"
  68,47,"Kaa …ďe anndu fii wirnii…ói …óin, hara hi…ďe winndira […óim hujjaaji ma…ď…ďe]"
  68,48,"Mu√Ī√Īor √Īaawoore Joomi maa nden, hara a wa'aali wa wonndii…óo linngii ngii fewndo o noddunoo [Joomi makko] himo sunii"
  68,49,"Si tawno mo∆ī∆īere immorde e Joomi makko hewtitanooki mo, ko pellet, o bugeteno e wulaa hara ko o felnii…óo"
  68,50,"Joomi makko su…ďii mo, O wa…ói mo e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen"
  68,51,"Hay yeddu…ďe …ďen e…ď…ďiinoo yuwirgol ma gite ma…ď…ďe …óen, nde …ďe nanunoo Janntoore nden, hi…ďe wi'a: \"On ko haangaa…óo"
  68,52,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] wonaali, si wanaa waaju tageefo ngon"
  69,1,Darngal
  69,2,Ko hon…óum woni Darngal
  69,3,Ko hon…óum anndin maa ko woni Darngal
  69,4,Samuudu e Aadi en fennii du…ó…óugol Darngal
  69,5,"Si ko Samuuda en, …ďe halkira haacaango"
  69,6,"Aadi en kan, …ďe halkira henndu bippooru hattinndu tii…óude"
  69,7,"O elti ndu e hoore ma…ď…ďe jemmaaji jee…ói…ói e √Īalormaaje jeetati jokkondir…óe; yi'aa yim…ďe …ďen no pukkii e …óin [ko…óooli] wa si tawii ko …ďe da∆ī∆īe tamaro irtii…óe"
  69,8,Taw si a yi'anay …ďe ko heddii
  69,9,Fir'awna e adinoo…ďe mo e ca'e junnitanoo…óe …óen ardi e goopi
  69,10,"…ďe yeddi Nulaa…óo Joomi ma…ď…ďe on, O nanngiri …ďe nanngal sattungal"
  69,11,"Ko Menen woni, fewndo ndiyam …óam hummbunoo, Min roondi on ka dogayka"
  69,12,"fii no Men wa…óirana …óum waaju, nowru nanayndu nana …óum"
  69,13,Si wuttaama ka allaandu wuttaande wootere
  69,14,leydi ndin e pelle …óen …ďamtee mo√Ī√Īe mo …ď√Ī√Īannde wootere
  69,15,"Nden √Īalnde, Darngal ngal daroto"
  69,16,"Kammu ngun seekoo, hara ko ngu lo'ungu nden √Īalnde"
  69,17,"Hara Malaa'ika'en wontira ka seraaji maggu, njeetato [e ma…ď…ďe] ronndoo Arsi Joomi maa kin e hoore ma…ď…ďe nden √Īalnde"
  69,18,Nden √Īalnde ko on wee…ďitetee; hay huunde e fii mon suu…óotaako
  69,19,"Si ko jonnitiroyaa…óo talkuru mun ndun ka √Īaamo mun, o wi'oyay : \"Ja…ďee ! Janngon talkuru am ndun"
  69,20,Min mi fellituno mi hawroygol e hasboore am mo∆ī∆īere nden
  69,21,Hara himo e nguurndam wel…óam
  69,22,E nder Aljanna toowu…óo
  69,23,mo dim…óe mun …ďadii
  69,24,"√Ďaamee yariron no newori, sabu ko ardin-…óon kon e √Īalaa…óe fe∆ī∆īu…óe"
  69,25,"Si tawii non ko jonntiiroyaa…óo talkuru mun ndun ka nano mun, on wi'oyay : \"Haaaniino lam hara mi jonnitaaka talkuru am ndun"
  69,26,Hara mi anndaali ko woni √Īaawoore am
  69,27,"Hara [maayde] nden wononu timmoode [am]"
  69,28,Jawdi am ndin duncanaali lam
  69,29,Mbaawko am kon halkirii lam
  69,30,Nanngee mo kolmbon bmo
  69,31,refti naadon mo ka Jahiimi
  69,32,refti naadon mo e jolokooje-callale- …óe juuteendi mun woni cogone cappan…óe jee…ói…ói
  69,33,Tawde o gom…óinaano Allah Maw…óo On
  69,34,O reer…óintaa e √Īammiingol miskiino
  69,35,Gi…óo …ďadondiraa…óo alanaamo …óoo hannde
  69,36,"wanaa √Īaametee, si wanaa e ∆īi∆ī∆īi∆īiri"
  69,37,"√Ďaamataa ndin, si wanaa bakkondim…ďe …ďen"
  69,38,Mi woondirii ko yi'oton kon
  69,39,E ko on yi'ataa kon
  69,40,"wonnde pellet, [Alqur'aana] ko konngol Nulaa…óo teddu…óo"
  69,41,wanaa nde konngu…ói yimoowo; kono fan…óii ko gom…óinton
  69,42,"wanaa kadi nde konngu…ói mbileejo, kono fam…óii ko waajitoto…óon"
  69,43,ko jippiniraande ka Jey…óo Winndere nden
  69,44,Si tawno o fefindino e Amen yoga e konngu…ói
  69,45,"ko pellet, Men nanngirayno mo doole"
  69,46,Hooti Men ta∆īayno e makko …óa…óol …ďernde ngol
  69,47,Alaa e mo'on hay gooto ha…óoowo Men e makko
  69,48,"Pellet, ndee [Alqur'aanaare] konde waajitorgol gom…óu…ďe …ďen"
  69,49,"Haray kadi, Me…óen anndi ina e mon fennoo…ďe [nde]"
  69,50,"ko pellet non, …óum ko nimse e hoore yeddu…ďe …ďen"
  69,51,"pellet kadi, ko nde goonga yananaa…óo"
  69,52,"Haray subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, Maw…óo On"
  70,1,Torotoo…óo torike lette yanay…óe
  70,2,"wonannde heefer…ďe …ďen, alaa du√Īanoowo …ďe …óe"
  70,3,"ko immorde ka Allah, Jom ∆īawru…óe"
  70,4,"Malaa'ka'en wonndude e Jibriilu hino ∆īawa faade e Makko, e nder √Īalaande nde e…ď…ďoore mun woni duu…ďi ujune cappan…óe jowi"
  70,5,"Mu√Ī√Īo tun, mu√Īal labaangal"
  70,6,Kam…ďe hi…ďe yi*a (lette) …óen ko wo…ó…óu…óe
  70,7,Me…óen reeni …óe Menen ko …ďadii…óe
  70,8,√Ďalnde kammu ngun wa'oyta wa ko taayinaa
  70,9,pelle …óen wa'oya wa hottolle kardaako
  70,10,ka …ďadondiraa…óo lamdotaako fii jeydaa…óo mun
  70,11,"Hi…ďe hollindiree. Bon…óo on yeloto sottorgol lette …óen nden √Īalnde, …ďi…ó…ďe makko …ďen"
  70,12,"e gennda makko, e neene gooto makko on"
  70,13,e gorol makko ngol moolayngol mo
  70,14,"e kala won…ďe ka leydi …ďen, fii no …óum da…óndira mo"
  70,15,"∆äum gasataa. Ngen [Yiite] ko uuyunge"
  70,16,…ďoltaynge guri hoore
  70,17,Hinge nodda on …óuurnii…óo o hucciti
  70,18,o moo…ďi (jawle) o mari e marirgel
  70,19,"Pellet, ne…ó…óo tagaama ko o …óen∆īotoo…óo"
  70,20,"si bone memii mo, o faaya"
  70,21,"si ko mo mo∆ī∆īere he…ďi mo, o salora"
  70,22,Si wanaa juuloo…ďe …ďen. @Corrected
  70,23,…ďen taw…ďe ko …ďe duumii…ďe e juulde ma…ď…ďe nden
  70,24,E …ďen taw…ďe hino ka jawle ma…ď…ďe haqqee anndaa…óo
  70,25,wonannde torotoo…óo e ha…óitii…ói
  70,26,e …ďen gom…óim…ďe √Īalaande njo…ďdi diina
  70,27,E …ďen taw…ďe ko …ďe hulu…ďe lette Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen
  70,28,"tawde pellet, lette Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen wanaa hoolnii…óe"
  70,29,E …ďen taw…ďe ko reenu…ďe farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin
  70,30,"si wanaa e rew…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa …ďen hor…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďe …ďe jeyiri √Īaame ma…ď…ďe, …óon on …ďe feletaake"
  70,31,"Kala non …óa…ď…ďu…óo [ka dakmitora] caggal …óum, haray ko …ďen woni jaggitu…ďe …ďen"
  70,32,E …ďen taw…ďe ko aynitu…ďe koolaaje e aadiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin
  70,33,E …ďen taw…ďe ko √Īii…ďu…ďe e seedeeji mun
  70,34,e …ďen taw…ďe ko reenoo…ďe e juulde ma…ď…ďe nden
  70,35,∆Āen …óon ko teddinoytee…ďe e Aljannaaji
  70,36,"E ko he…ďi yeddu…ďe …ďen takko maa…óa, hi…ďe he√Īora"
  70,37,"ka nano e ka √Īaamo, ko …ďe dentoy-dentoy"
  70,38,Hara gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe tam∆īinoto naatoygol Aljanna neemaaji
  70,39,∆äun wa…óataa ! Men tagiri…ďe ko …ďe anndi
  70,40,"Mi woondirii Jey…óo fu…óir…óe e mutir…óe On, pellet, ko Men hattan…ďe"
  70,41,"wattitirgol …ďe ko …ďuri …ďe mo∆ī∆īude, Men siforaa ronkugol […óum]"
  70,42,"Accu…ďe …ďe jumpa, …ďe fija haa …ďe hawroya e √Īalaande ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe kammbirananoo"
  70,43,"√Īalnde …ďe yaltiroyta e genaale …óen he√Īaare, wa si tawii ko kaa∆īe (sanamu) …ďe woni wugganaade"
  70,44,"Hara gite ma…ď…ďe no heli, koyeera no suddi …ďe. Ko nden √Īalaande woni ko …ďe kammbirananoo"
  71,1,"Men nulii Nuuhu haa e yim…ďe makko …ďen, wonnde : \"Jertin yim…ďe maa …ďen, ado lette muusu…óe arde e ma…ď…ďe"
  71,2,"O maakani […ďe] : \"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, min ko mi jertinoowo on …ďanngu…óo"
  71,3,"wonnde yo on rewu Allah, hulon Mo, …óofto…óon lam"
  71,4,"O haforanay on junuubi mon …óin, O nenna on haa e lajal ta∆īaangal. [Ko woni tun] lajal Allah ngal si hewtii, ngal nennetaake, si tawii hi…óon anndunoo"
  71,5,"O maaki : \"Joomi am, min mi noddirii yim…ďe am …ďen jemma e √Īalorma"
  71,6,"kono noddaandu am ndun …ďeydaali …ďe, si wanaa dogugol"
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi …ďe fii no Hafaranaa …ďe, …ďe wa…óay kolli ma…ď…ďe …óin ka nder noppi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe buumora comci ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďe deppitoo, …ďe townitora townitaadee"
  71,8,Refti mi noddirii …ďe e kene
  71,9,"Refti mi fe√Ī√Īinani …ďe, mi gunndii …ďe gunndaadee"
  71,10,"Mi wi'i […ďe] : \"Insinanee Joomi mon, tawde O siforii wonnde Haforoow"
  71,11,O wurtira to…ďo ngon e mo'on rewnindiral
  71,12,"O …ďeydira on jawle e …ďi…ó…ďe, O wa…óana on gese, O wa…óana on can…ói"
  71,13,"E ko he…ďi on, on jortaaki manngural Allah ngal"
  71,14,Hara le O tagir on taa…ďe-taa…ďe
  71,15,E on yi'aali no Allah tagiri kammuulli jee…ói…ói tegondir…ói
  71,16,"O wa…ói lewru ndun jal…ďundu e majji, O wa…ói naange ngen pitilol"
  71,17,Ko Allah fu…óniri on ka leydi fu…ónugol
  71,18,"refti O ruttiray on e mayri, O yaltina on yaltinndee"
  71,19,Allah wa…óiranii on leydi ndin weertaandi
  71,20,fii yo on naatir e mayri laawi yaaju…ói
  71,21,"Nuuhu maaki : \"Joomi am, …ďee yeddii lam, …ďe jokkii on mo jawle mun e …ďi…ó…ďe …ďeydaali …óum si wanaa hayrugol"
  71,22,∆Āe fewji feere mawnde
  71,23,"…ďe wi'i: \"Wata on terto dey rewetee…ói mon …óin: wata on terto Wudda, e Suwaa'a, e Ya'uuqatha, e Nasr"
  71,24,"Ko pellet, …ďe majjinii ko …óuu…ói. [Joomi] wata A …ďeydir too√Īu…ďe …ďen, si wanaa majjere"
  71,25,"Ko sagu goopi ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďe yooliranoo, …ďe naadaa Yiite, …ďe he…ďanaano ko'e ma…ď…ďe faabotoo…óo gaanin Allah"
  71,26,"Nuuhu maaki kadi : \"Joomi am, wata A accu e leydi ndin, hay keefeero dilloowo"
  71,27,"Ko pellet, si A accii …ďe, …ďe majjinay jeyaa…ďe Maa …ďen, …ďe jiidoytaako si wanaa bonnoo…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe geddi"
  71,28,"Joomi am, haforanam min e jibim…ďe lam …ďen, e …ďen gom…óim…ďe naatu…ďe ka suudu am, e gom…óim…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e gom…óim…ďe rew…ďe …ďen; wata A …ďeydir too√Īu…ďe …ďen, si wanaa halakuyee"
  72,1,"Maaku : \"Wahayinaama e am, wonnde dental jinna he…óino [lam mi…óo jannga Alqur'aana], …ói wi'i: \"Menen men nani janngeteende haawniinde"
  72,2,"Hinde …óowira e peewal. Men gom…óinii nde. Men kafidatah e Joomi amen, hay e gooto"
